WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.600
Mirror classroom setup:
rear wall, mirror, and viewer eye point.

00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:07.800
Green X is fixed at 75 cm.
Blue Y follows Y(d)=3d/(d+8) m.

00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:12.600
Move backward: d increases.
Dashed sight rays show why Y increases while X stays fixed.

00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:15.500
Conclusion:
X is constant, Y increases with d.
